  you feel more balanced and in control\, while the nearby Martin Commons 
 will have some yoga mats available for light stretching (when space allow
 s).  This group meets every Monday from 2-3 p.m.\, excluding holidays and
  museum closures. The group will meet in the Roehm Family Art-making Stud
 io\, located inside the Simpson Center for Education on the 2nd floor of 
 the Eskenazi Museum of Art.
