SUMMARY:Summer Art Camp: Teen Week
DESCRIPTION:Through a variety of hands-on experiences\, including drawing
 \, painting\, mixed media\, and more\, students will try new techniques\,
  work withdifferent materials\, and develop their own artistic style. By 
 the end of the week\, teens will leave with a collection of meaningful ar
 twork and fresh inspiration.  Art lessons and activities are thoughtfully
  designed and led by our licensed art educator.  Drop-off and pick-up inf
 ormation\, as well as teen driver information\, will be shared via email 
 after registration.12-3 pm Monday - Friday.
